Allot Products & Solutions
Intelligent IP Service Optimization and Revenue-Generation Solutions

Allot Communications is a leading global provider of intelligent broadband solutions that put mobile, fixed, and enterprise networks at the center of the digital lifestyle. The company's rich portfolio of high-performance platforms, integrated services, and insightful analytics empower network operators to shape digital lifestyle experiences and to capitalize on the network traffic they generate.
Allot products utilize open architecture and standard interfaces, allowing us to collaborate with leading solution providers and a growing cadre of service vendors in the digital lifestyle ecosystem, including SDN/NFV environments. Allot products and solutions are backed by a global support organization with technical experts in all regions providing 24/7 coverage. As a result, we deliver tangible results and create real value for our customers around the world.


Allot Products and Solutions

Service Gateway


High availability, reliability
Open architecture
Future-proof scalability



SG 9500


Cost-Efficient Performance
Accurate Traffic Visibility and Policy Control
Intelligent Policy and Charging Enforcement



NetEnforcer


Fail-safe performance
Service integration
Asymmetric traffic detection and QoS





Awareness & Analytics


Measure SLA performance over time
Customize usage reports for different audiences or users
Automatically generate and distribute reports to relevant audiences



Education


Troubleshoot and resolve performance degradation immediately
Protect your IT infrastructure from misuse and malicious DDoS attacks



Traffic Management


Optimize resource utilization and control costs
Assure seamless quality of experience across all access networks
Control congestion and eliminate sluggishness and downtime










