It’s your network. 
Know it. Control it.
Monetize it. Secure it. 

 

Read More 


 


 






Solutions for Service Providers
Allot multiservice solutions, powered by Allot Service Gateway, integrate essential capabilities across six domains:










Network Intelligence
Complete visibility and valuable insight on subscriber & application usage to drive business decisions










Security Services
Generate revenue from anti-malware, ad blocking, and parental controls delivered by your network










Policy Control & Charging
Increase revenue and customer loyalty through rapid rollout of differentiated service plans










DDoS Protection
Protect service availability & network resources from inbound and outbound Denial of Service attacks










Traffic Management
Optimize application performance and quality of experience for every user










VAS Delivery
Multiple options for rapid rollout of end to end VAS solutions






Solutions for Enterprises
Enabling organizations across various industries to improve productivity, protect network users, and cut costs, using:










Visibility
Gain complete visibility of users and applications on your network










Security
Protect your network and users with Web Security and DDoS Mitigation










Control
Improve application performance and QoE for every user






Success Stories
Allot multi service solutions and professional services help our customers achieve their business goals


  







Global CSP grabs mobile data market-share with zero-rated apps while preventing fraud and revenue leakage.


   







 “By keeping DDoS traffic off the network and managing CMTS congestion precisely where it occurs, we have been able to delay infrastructure expansion by 2 years and to save millions.” VOO, Belgium 


   







 “Allot solutions provide the visibility and control we need to ensure an excellent customer experience for every user of CRIF’s Web services.” Paulo Marino, CRIF IT Manager 


 



