	D.           



	Property, Plants and Equipment




	 






	Our principal administrative and research and development activities are located in approximately 72,000 square foot (6,700 square meter) facilities in Hod-Hasharon, Israel. The leases for our facilities vary in dates and terms, with the main facility’s lease commencing in July 2006 and expiring in June 2018.









	We also lease a 5,862 square foot (545 square meter) facility in Woburn, Massachusetts, for the purposes of our U.S. sales and marketing operations pursuant to a lease that expires in August 2019 and a 15,119 square foot (1,400 square meter) facility in San Diego, California for the purposes of our U.S research and development activities, which expires in April 2018. We lease other smaller facilities for the purpose of our development, sales and marketing and support activities in France, the United Kingdom, Italy, Germany, Singapore, Spain, China, Japan and New Zealand.



	 





	 






